OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTaliban bans Afghan female 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstaff, UN says             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The United Nations has said a Taliban  
OL,6, order has barred Afghan women from     
OL,7, working for the body.                  
OL,9,FThe UN said that while there has been  
OL,10,Fno written communication, the Taliban  
OL,11,Fhave informed them verbally.           
OL,13,FIt has told its Afghan staff - men and 
OL,14,Fwomen - to not report to work for 48   
OL,15,Fhours, until it has clarity on the     
OL,16,Fmatter in meetings with the Taliban.   
OL,18,FThere has been an increasing clampdown 
OL,19,Fon women's freedoms since the Taliban  
OL,20,Fseized power in 2021.                  
